Cherry Street, east from Jefferson Street. View 1 is across this thoroughfare; View 2 from a point slightly above; while the third is limited,showing buildings (No's. 28 to 294) at the N.E. corner. The vantage point for the latter is Water Street and the vacant lot extends on the east side of Jefferson Street.
Afril 23. 1939
Views: 1-2-3
P. L. Sperr
